com.jaxson.lib.io

Interface File<F extends File,R,W>

  • Type Parameters:
    F - the implementing Object for chaining
    R - the Object to be read
    W - the Object to write
    All Superinterfaces:
    Unwrapable<R>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DataFile, EmptyFile, ExcelFile, GdxFile, JsonFile

    public interface File<F extends File,R,W>
extends Unwrapable<R>
    A File that handles writing and reading.
